dc_title_s: Biscaia et Gvipvscoa: Cantabriae Veteris Pars Amstelodami, Apud Ioannem Iassonium.; Biscaia et Guipiscoa: Cantabria Veteris Pars
dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. Includes illustrations of ships in the ocean and a coats of arms. This state was published in the Atlas Novus by Jan Jansson circa 1680. From the Jansson Appendix Atlas 1636-1680, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan. 1 map; 37 x 48 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
dc_creator_sm: Jansson, Jan, 1588-1664.,Vignaud, Henry, 1830-1922, former owner.,Jansson, Jan, 1588-1664. Appendix Atlas.
